title: Yunlaiju - Windlucky - Dongmen
description: Name in Chinese is 云来居素食馆. Address in Chinese is 深圳罗湖区东门永新街东门町广场4楼(近地铁老街A出口). Yunnan style vegetarian dishes. Also serving a selection of pu'er tea. Buddhist veggy, no eggs used. Directions: Exit A of Laojie Station, Shenzhen Metro.
streetAddress: 4/F, Dongmen Ding Plaza, Yong Le Street, Dongmen, Luohu District, Guangdong
